    "name": "Roy",
    "epitet": "Blazing Lion",
    "display": "Roy: Blazing Lion",
    "description": "The son of the Marquess of Pherae. After overcoming misfortunes, he quells the uprising at Bern and ends the war between humans and dragons. Appears in Fire Emblem: The Binding Blade.",
    "artist": "Meka (めか)",
    "voiceActorEN": "Ray Chase",
    "voiceActorJP": "福山潤",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I am Roy, son of the Marquess of Pherae. If you need help, I'll lend you a hand. Together, we'll prevail!",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "A battle cannot be won alone. So many people support me that I can't even count them all. I am grateful to every single one of them. I must be.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "In the past, humans and dragons fought. But I believe it's always possible to reach an understanding.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You look a bit grim, friend. We're all here for you, so don't fret!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You can use magic, can you? My teacher told me I'm not cut out for it. Even so, I'd still like to try...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Just a little sword practice. I have a lot to learn, so I feel a lot of pressure to keep at it.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "My name is Roy, and I've been sent to greet you on behalf of <Friend Name>.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "The battle continues! I must have the strength to win it.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Not bad, but I can't let myself become complacent.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "No matter what befalls me, I must not be disheartened!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Thank you for that. I can feel the strength welling up within me. I will do well in my next battle.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "Because I won the war against Bern, people think of me as a great Hero. I think of it a little differently... A truly great Hero is one who can build a world where people can live completely free of care. A Hero is wise as well. There's so much to understand about the world, the citizens, and even the dragons. It's so much more complex than just being good with a sword. Coming to this world and getting to speak with so many Heroes—and also getting to know you—has inspired me. I want to learn even more from you. We can work together to shape the world. I'm counting on you! ",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
